<div class="home-hero">
  <h1>Welcome to Our Genealogy App</h1>
  <p class="subheading">Explore your family history and connect with your ancestors.</p>

  <div>
    <%= link_to 'Login', new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
  </div>
  <br />
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg">
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Build Your Legacy</h3>
          <p>Begin your journey into the past with our easy-to-use interface. Create your first profile and see how your family tree begins to take root. Perfect for beginners eager to document their heritage!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg">
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Discover Your Ancestry</h3>
          <p>Dive deeper into your family's history with advanced tools for exploring your ancestry. Uncover long-lost relatives and learn the stories of distant generations. It's your personal history book, waiting to be opened!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg">
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Connect and Collaborate</h3>
          <p>Bring your family together in this unique journey. Invite relatives to add their own branches, stories, and historical insights. Collaborate to complete the family mosaic and preserve your shared history for future generations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
